@* 查詢 / 篩選 / 每頁筆數工具列:純前端對已載入全量做(listQuery 接縫,見 docs/07 §5.3)。
   全量無資料時隱藏(由 dashboard.js 切換 hidden)。 *@
<section class="filterbar" id="filterbar" hidden aria-label="設備查詢與篩選">
    <input type="search" id="filter-q" class="filterbar__search"
           placeholder="搜尋設備名稱或編號…" aria-label="搜尋設備名稱或編號" autocomplete="off" />
    <div class="filterbar__group">
        <span class="filterbar__label">狀態</span>
        <div class="seg" id="filter-status" role="group" aria-label="依狀態篩選">
            <button type="button" class="seg__btn is-active" data-status="All">全部</button>
            <button type="button" class="seg__btn" data-status="Good">良好</button>
            <button type="button" class="seg__btn" data-status="Abnormal">異常</button>
            <button type="button" class="seg__btn" data-status="Danger">危險</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    @* 類型篩選:選項由 dashboard.js 依載入資料動態填入(有哪些類型就列哪些);與狀態/搜尋可疊加。 *@
    <div class="filterbar__group">
        <label class="filterbar__label" for="filter-type">類型</label>
        <select id="filter-type" class="filterbar__select" aria-label="依設備類型篩選">
            <option value="All" selected>全部類型</option>
        </select>
    </div>
    <div class="filterbar__group filterbar__group--end">
        <label class="filterbar__label" for="filter-sort">排序</label>
        <select id="filter-sort" class="filterbar__select" aria-label="排序方式">
            <option value="severity" selected>嚴重度</option>
            <option value="name">名稱</option>
            <option value="value">最新值</option>
        </select>
        <button type="button" id="filter-sort-dir" class="filterbar__sortdir" aria-label="目前降冪,點擊改升冪" title="升冪 / 降冪">↓</button>
        <label class="filterbar__label" for="filter-page-size">每頁</label>
        <select id="filter-page-size" class="filterbar__select" aria-label="每頁顯示筆數">
            <option value="12" selected>12 筆</option>
            <option value="24">24 筆</option>
            <option value="48">48 筆</option>
        </select>
        <span class="filterbar__count" id="filter-count" aria-live="polite"></span>
    </div>
</section>
